name: Guest of Cindy Sherman
description: A documentary on art-scene commentator Paul Hasegawa-Overacker's relationship with enigmatic photographer Cindy Sherman.

review.author: whatithinkis
review.heading: Were I Cindy Sherman, et al
review.reviewBody: I would do everything I could to expunge this . . . pedestrian . . . thing . . . from EVERYwhere. It more reduces than increases the invaluable mysteries.
